{"tid":1886502,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威天才夏蘭特：我同5個女人一齊瞓覺！","createTime":"2020-02-19T02:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T03:59:26.000Z","uid":47132,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4e1eb60791620567810d60feb023ab2a2bfc33","tid":1886502,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191114/photo/bkn-20191114160138125-1114_00882_001_01p.jpg?20191114170429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20191114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191114160138125-1114_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20191114170429&h=83e81d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際賽檔期展開，挪威超新星夏蘭特返到國家隊，準備周五對法羅群島嘅歐國外賽事，呢位前鋒今季已經演出5個帽子戲法，亦喺歐聯射手榜領先，佢接受挪威傳媒訪問表示，足球係佢女朋友。<br />\n夏蘭特表示，每次帽子戲法後都會帶個足球返屋企，然後攬住瞓，佢話：「現時屋企嘅足球愈嚟愈多，我每日都會同5個足球一齊瞓，因為入波嘅感覺實在太好喇。」<br />\n作為一位新星，夏蘭特並非一位賴床嘅人，攬住5個波瞓覺都唔會瞓過龍，因為佢有個鬧鐘，響聲唔係一般鈴聲，而係歐聯開場音樂，一聽到歐聯音樂，佢就會立即起身！"},{"pid":"a56bfa48f37625a388322b79624f43dd7c74cb3d","tid":1886502,"uid":125724,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"另類毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afeb00704f5b195b0c00991b945b2d29c3af7d2","tid":1886502,"uid":46904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"唔怪得場場都射入"},{"pid":"4cc6295a8f4b4c37066d1005a7f1d1704b5fd75d","tid":1886502,"uid":4957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"唐士"},{"pid":"47ed05a649d8cf1030f985d0f1eb83f7512e1868","tid":1886502,"uid":43718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"如果靚仔啲就一流"},{"pid":"a9a3195962c7e148d3959b8e28f6e7d372b4a1f7","tid":1886502,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"功夫足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a959f5ccb8d5eb60c144661cdfc9